Linux2, Linux2023 fluent-bit 설치 패키지
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fluent/fluent-bit/master/install.sh | sh

사이트
https://docs.fluentbit.io/manual/installation/linux/amazon-linux#amazon-linux-2022


설치
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fluent/fluent-bit/master/install.sh | sh
sudo systemctl start fluent-bit
sudo systemctl enable fluent-bit
sudo systemctl restart fluent-bit
sudo systemctl status fluent-bit.service

편집 경로
vi /etc/fluent-bit/fluent-bit.conf
vi /etc/fluent-bit/parsers.conf
